<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Apr1937"><font color="red">27 April 1937</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  Mr Eliot asked me to acknowledge with thanks your letter and the list of misprints in the typescript of WORK IN PROGRESS. We are sending another set of galley proofs to Mr Joyce directly, and will have the misprints corrected. </div>
